snippet.title: Adventuring With Matilda! - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Step into the shoes of an aspiring adventurer and delve into a perilous dungeon alongside Matilda, a beautiful elf with a secret, exploring and deepening your bond through shared trials and bonding moments.

Adventuring With Matilda! on Kagura Games Store: https://www.kaguragames.com/product/adventuring-with-matilda/

Adventuring With Matilda! on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3329430/Adventuring_With_Matilda/
